        <section class="description_contact ">
      <h1>問い合わせフォーム</h1>
      <p>何かご不明な点、質問等ありましたら下記のフォームよりお問い合わせください</p>
      <article>
        <form class="form-horizontal col-sm-offset-1 center-block" action="/contact_submit" method="post" onsubmit="return conrimMessage();">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="control-label col-sm-3" for="name"><p style="margin-left:30px;">お名前</p></label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="form-control" placeholder="お名前" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="control-label col-sm-3" for="address"><p>連絡先</p></label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <input type="email" id="address" name="address" size="20" maxlength="40" class="form-control" placeholder="メールアドレス" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="control-label col-sm-3 col-xs-10" for="password"><p class="label_form2"></p></label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <input type="text" id="address" name="tel" class="form-control" placeholder="電話番号">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="col-sm-3 control-label" for="InputTextarea">内容</label>
              <div class="col-sm-6">
                <textarea placeholder="ここに問い合わせ内容を書き込んでください。" rows="5" class="form-control" name='contents' id="InputTextarea" required></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group submit">
                <div class="col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
                    <input type="submit" value="送信" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
                </div>
            </div>
            <input id="token" type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= reqCsrf %>">
        </form>
      </article>
    </section>
